{"tid":2334940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府歡迎終審法院裁決　批評蒙面違法者損害法治","createTime":"2020-12-21T12:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T03:05:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"996e075f19a9dd85306245c9da448c4b7aaa5ea0","tid":2334940,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"政府歡迎終審法院裁定《緊急條例》和《禁蒙面規例》合憲。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，裁決確立《緊急條例》符合《基本法》，以及《禁蒙面規例》符合相稱性的要求，政府完全同意終審法院所指，在尋求社會利益和個人權利之間要取得公正平衡時，亦需考慮香港整體利益，批評蒙面違法者隱藏身分，以為不用受到法律制裁而違法，屬於損害法治。<br />\n<br />\n政府認為，終審法院認同《禁蒙面規例》的預防和阻嚇性質十分關鍵，認為避免和平的公眾集結，演變成暴力衝突，屬規例正當目的之核心部分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566489-20201221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566489-20201221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=33dc528d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566489-20201221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9fb9df9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566489-20201221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9dd0ee7856f4841c52075753e96f84de4afd8075","tid":2334940,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"哂撚氣"},{"pid":"279f0a3989d638d34f221981b0467ccd1ed2283c","tid":2334940,"uid":65888,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"岩牙，d蒙面違法者仲要個個無number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c289a8afe1347bf1db50fb57ce1eecf72efaa5","tid":2334940,"uid":76804,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCDeAtN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCDeAtN.png&h=056b59e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b485ca3355e5a30b48e789f3eb080